        "title": "",
        "html": "<h2>Ultimate Protection</h2>\n\n<p>Our safety equipment is designed to provide the highest level of protection against workplace hazards. From hard hats and safety goggles to gloves and ear protection, our gear ensures you are well-protected in any situation. Made from robust, high-quality materials, DNC Safety Equipment is built to withstand the toughest conditions, offering reliable protection day after day.</p>\n\n<h2>Ergonomic and Comfortable Design</h2>\n\n<p>Safety is paramount, but comfort is also crucial. Our safety equipment features ergonomic designs that ensure a comfortable fit, even during long work hours. Adjustable elements and lightweight materials reduce fatigue, allowing you to stay focused and productive while staying protected.</p>\n\n<h2>Durable and Reliable</h2>\n\n<p>DNC Direct safety equipment is constructed from durable materials that provide long-lasting performance. Whether you’re working in construction, manufacturing, or any high-risk industry, our gear is designed to endure the rigours of daily use. When you choose DNC Safety Equipment, you are investing in products known for their exceptional durability and reliability.</p>\n\n<h2>Comprehensive Range</h2>\n\n<p>Our collection includes a wide variety of safety gear to meet all your needs. From head protection and eye protection to respiratory and hearing protection, DNC Direct has you covered. Each product is meticulously designed to offer the best in safety and functionality, ensuring you have the right equipment for any job.</p>\n\n<span id=\"dots\">...</span><span id=\"more\">\n\n<h2>Trusted Quality</h2>\n\n<p>At DNC Direct, we prioritise quality and compliance with safety standards. Our safety equipment undergoes rigorous testing to meet and exceed Australian safety regulations. When you choose DNC Safety Equipment, you can trust that you are getting gear that delivers the highest level of protection and performance.</p>\n\n<h2>Exceptional Value</h2>\n\n<p>We believe that top-quality safety equipment should be accessible to everyone. Our collection offers a variety of products at competitive prices, ensuring you get the best value for your money. Each piece of equipment is designed to provide excellent protection, comfort, and durability without compromising on quality.</p>\n\n<h2>Shop with Confidence</h2>\n\n<p>Explore the DNC Direct Safety Equipment Collection today and experience the best in protective gear. Shop with confidence, knowing that you are supporting a 100% Australian owned business dedicated to delivering superior safety equipment. Join the DNC Direct family and step into a world of quality, reliability, and unparalleled protection.</p>\n\n<h2>Features and Benefits:</h2>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n<strong>High-Quality Materials:</strong> Ensures maximum protection and durability.</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Ergonomic Design:</strong> Provides comfort and reduces fatigue during long hours.</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Comprehensive Protection:</strong> Covers head, eye, ear, and respiratory safety needs.</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Adjustable Fit:</strong> Customisable for a comfortable and secure fit.</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Meets Australian Safety Standards:</strong> Guarantees top-level quality and protection.</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Wide Range of Products:</strong> Offers solutions for various safety requirements.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n\n<p><strong>Q: What types of safety equipment are available in the DNC Direct Safety Equipment Collection?</strong></p>\n<p>A: Our collection includes hard hats, safety goggles, gloves, ear protection, respiratory masks, and more. Each product is designed to provide the best in safety and functionality.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Q: Is DNC Safety Equipment suitable for construction and industrial work?</strong></p>\n<p>A: Yes, our safety equipment is designed to meet the needs of high-risk industries, including construction and industrial work, ensuring maximum protection in demanding environments.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Q: How should I care for my safety equipment?</strong></p>\n<p>A: To maintain the quality and effectiveness of your safety gear, follow the manufacturer’s care instructions. Regularly inspect your equipment for signs of wear and replace any damaged items promptly.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Q: What is the return policy for DNC Safety Equipment?</strong></p>\n<p>A: We offer a hassle-free return policy within 30 days of purchase. Please visit our returns page for more information.</p>\n\n<p><strong>We provide the best quality PPE including Gloves and Protective Eyewear</strong></p>\n\n</span>\n\n<strong><button onclick=\"myFunction()\" id=\"myBtn\">Read more</button></strong>\n\n<style>\n#more {display: none;}\n</style>\n\n\n<script>\nfunction myFunction() {\n  var dots = document.getElementById(\"dots\");\n  var moreText = document.getElementById(\"more\");\n  var btnText = document.getElementById(\"myBtn\");\n\n  if (dots.style.display === \"none\") {\n    dots.style.display = \"inline\";\n    btnText.innerHTML = \"Read more\"; \n    moreText.style.display = \"none\";\n  } else {\n    dots.style.display = \"none\";\n    btnText.innerHTML = \"Read less\"; \n    moreText.style.display = \"inline\";\n  }\n}\n</script>"
      }
